02466e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9438be88-9574-42dc-9b9f-b3f6a8695bfe\" style=\"color:#555555;\">상황의 개인적인 취향을</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-28e77e70-4a18-4c50-9a0d-5eb9a257aa44\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-15ea94b2-87fa-4171-aaed-b3ed614e2497\" style=\"color:#555555;\">배제하더라도</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-10b71000-21fe-4493-86c7-afe841da7655\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ed23ce1a-e5b9-4ffb-91b9-f025495ca94c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">요즘 트렌드는 조금은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0d2eaeab-b8b8-494d-bce8-3547d7499c5e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4b2cfc0d-027a-4e90-bdb3-002f4b798da0\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">두꺼운 명함을 선호</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4bf160c6-3523-4307-8600-344d61965eca\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하는 것처럼</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-dfc1bf4f-8a44-406c-bcd9-e63f2d0ce0fd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2c327585-cdab-41eb-a6b5-60b314dfda36\" style=\"color:#555555;\">보입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e2831a5f-4614-480b-b545-d209a6855b83\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e5db1749-0642-43dc-917f-7f0380d636bc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-37c230e7-de97-490c-aae0-cdc8ab017014\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2d6ca26c-dfce-43db-a91d-de15abb6993c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 이유로 여러 회사에서</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6b9a23b8-aea2-4a6d-a6ff-4c4488f8d9fd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a3befbd1-dabf-4c98-9489-c2a991f65bbb\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>두꺼운 평량의 명함</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8a58158b-b0f1-4569-8611-bc6a70d05599\" style=\"color:#555555;\">을</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c8a95b46-ee9b-4ef4-a5fa-3c88554aabb4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-59f16d04-fa5a-446a-b9e9-3750237973d1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">출시하고 있는 상황입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8c8fca44-f206-4559-9f63-1091288d6d3a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b7dd4e95-6249-48fa-b06c-8b7054764641\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-385d5b9b-0d13-40bb-9b0a-0b75d3a1e11b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-21a75173-da54-4d25-88b7-917ceea4b1e8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">저희 쿡 더디자 인도</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4dd07bc3-ce48-4d72-92bd-75ebad63746c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f777a63e-b04b-4774-b6ac-d2e81a84188b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">고평량의 종이를</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d78fd18a-0562-4faf-b70f-e67e2f9127e8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c0f8de5a-e233-4e00-a2dc-5448f510d87e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">선별하여 고객 여러분께</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-882e9d94-33b4-4712-a1e0-33a603bcd44f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-be3dbf3a-f955-485c-a5f0-d2f44ad74796\" style=\"color:#555555;\">납품해 드리고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-733fdc1b-a091-41c9-87dd-16f28b60f14f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-9772098e-2d04-4ed2-99bc-c3d09703f2a1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b959b7ed-d038-4914-aaa5-ea29baaade24\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-8bdf1e31-8c35-419f-81d5-d9c25bf39f75\" style=\"\">고평량 종이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-84d6155c-40d7-45e0-95d2-f81e5622a504\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-96fb1313-c2ab-4451-a719-7ded0921c9d4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-25ad1b37-bec5-4998-8302-c210cd8bea35\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>· 아르떼 울트라화이트 310g</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-cfaf892b-bf09-4aca-a99a-94db2fe7cb1b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d2afac62-048c-4201-b895-4ce21e769976\" style=\"color:#555555;\">대표적인 고평량 종이입니다. 국내에서 생산되는 종이로 가격도 비교적 저렴하면서 인쇄 색감도 잘 표현해 주는 만능 같은 용지입니다. 명함뿐 아니라 리플렛이나 기타 용도로도 사용이 가능합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bb5ee821-9415-4d04-8aad-a15344057818\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223768331396/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9ff575c8-f3df-43bc-97a6-737bf0c34fcb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-9abae424-5500-40f5-a881-1ff81812f2c6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d9388a67-5ed9-49c5-9d82-297732415735\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-0a00650e-16c1-46fa-83c8-0c222e3d4fab\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6fb0fcce-ef1e-4432-8540-77f6a16c0500\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>· 아코팩/올드밀 화이트 300g</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-57d2973f-a090-4dbe-b195-bb1ae5ea22c8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a4168298-c584-47fc-be59-9b7bdb4cc3d7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">대표적인 고평량 종이들은 대부분 백색이나 고백색을 띠고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-92066e90-df5c-4e55-99a0-fb58a6365652\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-52f9720b-4c04-4aa5-87a8-3bc24b7098a3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-b424aced-8014-4bea-b333-b9eb42dc8927\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-50fd5832-c63e-4190-9048-dd0c0f62ecdc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">물론 색지 중에 고평량의 종이로 생산하는 경우도 많습니다. 그 대표적인 종이가 검은색 종이류입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-065843cc-e642-47c3-a6e1-96fd5e68c710\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223768331396/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b40e8cf0-303e-44c5-875a-47f3bc97f2ed\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-2c41da3d-3001-4b21-912e-51ecf4d1fe0c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-010c1587-f7e4-4945-b018-26c4f1c191da\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-b9f6f85b-dc85-4330-ba5f-22196bbebdcd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e7e19e63-fae3-4688-95d0-31f82e0db006\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>· 시리오 칼라 시리즈 290g(검정 외 3가지 색상)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-79271eb7-3693-46a0-9b69-09256760e0dc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0b42fbe6-0969-4721-9f58-77e1f8d0c9f6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">검정색지 명함은 백색 인쇄만 가능할 수 있습니다. 다른 색상을 원하신다면 별도의 견적으로 진행되며 일반적인 가격보다 훨씬 비쌀 수 있습니다. 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-366545a0-e514-47a0-ad11-793eeca6d6ac\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6d8d7f64-5237-4c5a-a33d-ce2b1c10ed15\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-d0549ca2-d23b-4550-848c-b48b317e49f1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b3bde030-d5ec-464c-8095-12b71f2cede3\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>· 기타 500g 이상 특수 박인쇄 명함</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-d6e2327a-0868-48c5-aa53-bded2ec09dbf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a349c73b-4c40-488d-80b2-5634c3c92ff8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">보다 더 특별한 명함을 원하는 고객이 늘어남에 따라 완전히 두꺼운 500g이상의 종이에 박이나 형압으로만 인쇄하는 경우도 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-ddb61d18-b9f6-4e95-ab08-89b09b761eba\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9e4c7c93-b7ec-47c2-9526-820bdc94dc2d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">단 인쇄는 불가능할 수 있으니 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ba041e51-e6bb-4a5b-a9d8-d915cb3a1116\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223768331396/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-18d60080-37b1-4ba2-824d-40e1e08c9489\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-03052ed5-3881-445e-b192-81c6451fc701\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-15a512d1-9746-493a-bbda-19fc5f45d7d7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-a8813579-d7f9-45cc-b87e-bf287c8a5387\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-db36f1b9-8846-46ca-b4d0-941da36b6206\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-42aedbaf-4cc3-4659-9370-14ab8f65900b\" style=\"\">고평량 명함 인쇄</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c16fad9a-b8d1-461b-ae42-a26d3863a991\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-b71ba989-9d1d-4e26-9967-11a27ce027c8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-34ae311a-0a67-4ca1-9016-5a69b6d350cb\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>· 칼라인쇄</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-f0eb706e-2903-44cc-a757-05ec23dde6c8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fb475337-fce8-4616-b9ec-4ab3dbaa7525\" style=\"color:#555555;\">4도 칼라와 특별한 경우 별색인쇄도 진행이 가능합니다. 다만 이런 경우 엄청나게 많은 비용이 명함 값으로 지불하게 됩니다. 그래도 자신 회사만의 퀄리티와 특별함을 강조하고 싶으시다면 상담해 주시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-908202cd-f394-4788-963d-5f178e170826\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f289195f-9646-4e55-b3e9-211cc3629d99\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-f9acee41-063f-4b50-aa0d-e3e05ec87219\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-768bfd86-ea8a-48cc-8848-d9660108928b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>· 백색인쇄</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-90f8ccee-f763-4773-8157-517960a3d736\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-63dece1a-2023-4f77-b650-af8e62f5f07c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">색지인 경우 주로 백색인쇄를 진행합니다. 백색은 특별히 정교한 인쇄가 불가능할 수 있으므로 작은 서체 폰트나 얇은 선은 제약될 수 있으니 반드시 상담 후 진행하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7310dd75-a421-44bc-8457-be57f0da5964\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223768331396/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6921cfe0-e65f-4227-a2ba-d659dc6b2aca\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a84299b0-e448-46d2-9faa-a30034317f0e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a4c8329f-d63f-4477-8e93-57075e4d0e7f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-277a92f1-616a-4dae-87d6-fb712f9fba63\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d1a87cfa-91c3-4d0f-b987-a28f363b2b57\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-cd967737-de4c-4e44-bf00-0624c6ab94f4\" style=\"\">고평량 명함 후공정</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0a5134f7-fdc3-403d-a7a2-a21239915f3f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-894ae3ac-8cad-43e4-9add-175ccf1ad7bb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e8cd25b5-5864-473e-a758-a06da24bf7aa\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>· 박인쇄</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-7a759066-2d96-4410-9741-3a3999d18758\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1b8c73bb-e5bf-4493-97ba-18b7d1ef9118\" style=\"color:#555555;\">주로 고평량명함으로 진행하실 경우 후공정으로 박인쇄를 진행합니다. 금박이나 은박이 기본이고 그 외에 특별한 박인쇄도 진행이 가능합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-5126c53c-1157-419e-b0a7-567f60eaadd1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-64d417b8-7bec-4ad2-af54-4078e86069ca\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-a6b74e72-38b7-432a-abf4-774807e1456b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c4474c1b-2127-4a60-96cd-000886179635\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>· 형압</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-ddb30f6a-6486-4dc0-89ef-d6488e953dad\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e9d77232-db63-4c46-b78c-be559c53f2ab\" style=\"color:#555555;\">형압은 로고 주변에 돌출을 묘사하는 작업입니다. 이런 작업으로 이루어지면 높은 퀄리티의 명함으로 인식될 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-23812751-dfe2-47b5-9ae2-6c48a0920091\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ee4ebf3b-1ab7-4c99-b43a-3b1b434872f9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-da7d5137-90cc-47e1-87ae-73af5e88a9bc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8ead2f38-2456-482c-896a-279efb162d7c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>· 기타</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-8cc60302-a2b4-467f-b034-c559222d18a1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-99a2281b-976c-42a1-907b-d34d32a22757\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그 외에 에폭시나 도무송 등 다양한 방법으로 명함을 만들 수 있습니다. 문의나 소통 없이 가격대만 믿고 재작업 사고로 이어지는 오류를 범하지 마시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f4579360-1560-409e-b428-034603d795c0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223768331396/006.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a03a57ec-e857-4885-a20f-2f3999699b8d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-bad1e5d0-80b8-4e6f-a6e9-8725bd441432\" style=\"\">에폭시</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f7d2df64-0103-4f18-b419-184777f8a787\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-0a9829d5-83c9-4706-937f-4d8313dd4e0f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7235384a-5fea-42a9-8a22-ef1ef49b30df\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-7b5894f1-15fb-4f37-83e8-24bf26f16ea4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a8d7647c-dfd0-4cfb-bda1-44c02b9ca5b7\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>반드시 상담 후 진행을 추천드립니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1418b90c-befd-4fc1-8b9e-69500b0bf9bc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
